BAIM - BitchX AIM Client Module

********** Installation ********************
# Note: x.xx == version number (ie. "0.4a")
cp baim-x.xx.tar.gz BitchX/dll
(cd BitchX/dll; tar zxvf baim-x.xx.tar.gz)
cd BitchX
./configure --with-plugins=baim-x.xx
(cd BitchX/dll/baim-x.xx;./configure)
make install
********** Good Luck ***********************

********** Running *************************
/loaddll baim

Commands:
ωνω aaway           aback           aclose          addbuddy
ωνω aim             aimidle         aw              awho
ωνω delbuddy        im              showlist

	/aaway		[reason]		Set away on aim
	/aback					Unset away
	/aclose					Close connection to aim
	/addbuddy	[group] [screenname]	Addbuddy to buddy list
	/aim					Connect to aim
	/aimidle 	[idle minutes]		Set idle minutes
	/aw					Show buddy's on your list that
						are currently online
	/awho		[screenname]		Get buddy information
	/delbuddy	[screenname]		delete buddy from list
	/im		[screenname]		Send im to [screenname]
	/showlist				Ugly listing of all users in
						buddy list
********** fun stuff ***********************

Logging in:
/set aim_screenname <screenname>
/set aim_password <password>
/aim

